description: A front end for the Nextcloud Bookmark app An Android front end for the Nextcloud/Owncloud Bookmark App based on the new REST API that was introduced by Bookmarks version 0.10.1 With this app you can add/edit/delete and view bookmarks, and sync them with your Nextcloud. However you need to have the Bookmarks app in minimal required version 0.10.1 installed and enabled on you Nextcloud. If you need more information about the Nextcloud Bookmark app, you can follow this link: https://apps.nextcloud.com/apps/bookmarks
